{
  "stem": "8703.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was going on for some times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never find out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, I found out why he could do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I said-- after a while I said, you know, the 13-- hala 13, the hall 13, that they are producing, the, the, the pickrin, the yellow stuff, over there it was Professor [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ringel ?] in charge of the production like I was here in charge, Professor Ringel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- I spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he found out that we are doing less, 14 boxes instead 15.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, please, Kaminsky, find out if he will do it also for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I asked him the following day, would you do it for, for the hala-- for the hall 13 with pickrin, and work with Professor Ringel?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, I'll try.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll see what I can do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After a while, he did also with Professor Ringel from the hall 13.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a bigger place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had only three presses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had five or six presses, twice as much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was some relief also for the people, for these yellow people from this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a tremendous thing for them especially, because they were exhausted people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after a while, something happened that we couldn't believe that it will come to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Jewish man went to the Germans, to the hala 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he reported what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess-- I was told later on-- later on, I found out how this man was OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a Pollack by the name [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kopetsky ?], who was a Polish man, who spoke German very well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the beginning we thought maybe he's a German, a volksdeutsche we used to call him.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
